Package: ggerror
Title: Modified Error Geoms for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yann", "Cohen", , "yannco5@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-0509-3609"))
Description: Unifies the 'ggplot2' error geoms behind a single layer,
    geom_error(), that accepts an 'error' aesthetic, infers orientation
    from the data, computes min/max bounds, and dispatches to
    geom_errorbar(), geom_linerange(), geom_crossbar(), or
    geom_pointrange(). Adds support for asymmetric errors
    via 'error_neg' and 'error_pos' aesthetics, including one-sided error bars.
